RS PRO RS14 Digital Multimeter
The RS PRO RS14 digital multimeter (DMM) is a handheld tool which can measure capacitance, voltage,
electrical current and resistance with diode and continuity check. There is also a “hold” function available
in the compact design making it very user-friendly. The multimeter is also CAT III rated for 600V.
